content.html: Matt Hancock on I’m a Celeb is a political move. He is reinventing himself after the appalling way he handled being a senior minister in the pandemic. He dehumanised the population, and now wants you to see him in a better light for his own career & gain. #ImACeleb
content.value:
Matt Hancock on I’m a Celeb is a political move.

He is reinventing himself after the appalling way he handled being a senior minister in the pandemic.

He dehumanised the population, and now wants you to see him in a better light for his own career & gain. 

#ImACeleb
